    <title>深搜</title>
    <link href="/2025/12/23/%E6%B7%B1%E6%90%9C/"/>
    <url>/2025/12/23/%E6%B7%B1%E6%90%9C/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="指数型枚举"><a href="#指数型枚举" class="headerlink" title="指数型枚举"></a>指数型枚举</h2><h3 id="问题模型："><a href="#问题模型：" class="headerlink" title="问题模型："></a><strong>问题模型：</strong></h3><p>$n$个数字，每个数字是$1 \sim m$，按字典序从小到大输出</p><p>例如：$n&#x3D;3$   $m&#x3D;4$</p><p>$1 1 1 1$</p><p>$1112$</p><p>$1113$</p><p>$…$</p><p>$4444$ </p><h3 id="代码实现"><a href="#代码实现" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a><strong>代码实现</strong></h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++">如果用普通的<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>循环来实现<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=m ; i++)&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; j&lt;=m ; j++)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> k=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; k&lt;=m ; k++)&#123;<br>            ....<br>            一直嵌套n层为止<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><br>但我们并不知道n有多大，所以我们可以用递归的方式解决<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x[];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">dfs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 第k层循环  为第k个位置做选择</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(k&gt;n)&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">// 递归出口</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=n ; i++) cout&lt;&lt;x[i];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=m ; i++)&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 1~m 进行选择</span><br> x[k]=i;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 没有i,j,k..这些变量进行记录，所以需要把每层循环的选择记下来</span><br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">dfs</span>(k<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="排列"><a href="#排列" class="headerlink" title="排列"></a>排列</h2><h3 id="问题模型：-1"><a href="#问题模型：-1" class="headerlink" title="问题模型："></a><strong>问题模型：</strong></h3><p>$1\sim n $中选 $m$ 个数字的排列</p><p>例如：$n&#x3D;3$  $m&#x3D;2$</p><p>$1\ 2$</p><p>$1\ 3$</p><p>$2\ 1$</p><p>$2\ 3$</p><p>$3\ 1$</p><p>$1\ 2$</p><h3 id="代码实现-1"><a href="#代码实现-1" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a><strong>代码实现</strong></h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++">如果用<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>循环来实现<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=n ; i++)&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; j&lt;=n ; j++)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(j != i)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> k=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; k&lt;=n ; k++)&#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(k != i &amp;&amp; k != j)&#123;<br>                    .....<br>                    嵌套m层循环<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br>但我们并不知道m有多大，所以我们可以用递归的方式解决<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x[],vis[];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">dfs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 第k层循环    为第k个位置做选择</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(k&gt;m)&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">// 递归出口</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=m ; i++) cout&lt;&lt;x[i];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=n ; i++)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( !vis[i] )&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 和之前的区别  要先判断数字i在之前并没有被选择</span><br>            vis[i]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 标记</span><br>            x[k]=i;<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">dfs</span>(k<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>);<br>            vis[i]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;   <span class="hljs-comment">//回溯！！！重中之中  继续循环，相当于重新选择，那么要把刚刚打的标记去掉</span><br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="组合"><a href="#组合" class="headerlink" title="组合"></a>组合</h2><h3 id="问题模型：-2"><a href="#问题模型：-2" class="headerlink" title="问题模型："></a><strong>问题模型</strong>：</h3><p>$1 \sim n$ 中选 $m$ 个数字的组合（不考虑元素顺序）</p><p>组合与排列的核心区别是<strong>不考虑元素的选取顺序</strong>，仅关注选取的元素集合。只要保持元素递增（或者是元素下标递增），即可避免重复的情况。</p><p>例如：$n &#x3D; 3$    $ m &#x3D; 2$</p><p>$1 \  2$</p><p>$1 \ 3$</p><p>$2 \ 3$</p><h3 id="代码实现-2"><a href="#代码实现-2" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a><strong>代码实现</strong></h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++">如果用<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>循环来实现<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i&lt;=n; i++)&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=i<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>; j&lt;=n; j++)&#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// j从i+1开始，避免重复组合</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 若m=3，需再嵌套一层for(k=j+1; k&lt;=n; k++)</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 嵌套m层循环，m未知时无法编写</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 嵌套m层循环，m不确定时无法实现</span><br><br>递归实现<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x[],vis[];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">dfs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 第k层循环    为第k个位置做选择</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(k&gt;m)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> ; i&lt;=m ; i++) cout&lt;&lt;x[i];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=x[k<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]<span class="hljs-number">+1</span> ; i&lt;=n ; i++)&#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">//x[k-1]即存了上一层循环的数字</span><br>        x[k]=i;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">dfs</span>(k<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="问题变式"><a href="#问题变式" class="headerlink" title="问题变式"></a>问题变式</h3><p>洛谷 P1025 数的划分  </p><p>将整数 $n$ 分成 $k$ 份，且每份不能为空，任意两个方案不相同（不考虑顺序）。</p><p>$n&#x3D;7$    $k&#x3D;3$</p><p>$1,1,5$</p><p>$1,2,4$</p><p>$1,3,3$</p><p>$2,2,3$</p><p>思路：参考排列的思想，让每份数保持<strong>非降</strong>即可，多了一个总和的限制。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x[<span class="hljs-number">200</span>],sum=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,n,m;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">dfs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> k,<span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt)</span></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(k&gt;m)&#123;      <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果没有数量限制  只有和的限制  把这个if删除即可</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(cnt==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) sum++;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=x[k<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>];i&lt;=cnt;i++)&#123;<br>x[k]=i;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">dfs</span>(k<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>,cnt-i);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>&#123;<br>cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;m;<br>    x[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;     <span class="hljs-comment">// 保持每份非空</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">dfs</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,n); <br>cout&lt;&lt;sum;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
